{
  "id": "hzn-kpe-2wp",
  "title": "Infinity Embedding Server",
  "description": "Industry-standard monitoring dashboard for the Infinity embedding inference server (infinity-prod-deploy) on AKS GPU spot nodes in divyam-prod-k8s-cluster. Covers the RED method (Rate, Errors, Duration), resource utilization, and Python runtime health for degradation detection.",
  "author_handle": "rbharathkumar0409@gmail.com",
  "author_name": "Bharath Kumar",
  "layout_type": "ordered",
  "url": "/dashboard/hzn-kpe-2wp/infinity-embedding-server",
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "handler",
      "prefix": "handler",
      "available_values": [
        "/embeddings",
        "/health",
        "/metrics"
      ],
      "defaults": [
        "/embeddings",
        "/health",
        "/metrics"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "host",
      "prefix": "host",
      "available_values": [
        "aks-gpu-spot-glnw5-divyam-prod-k8s-cluster",
        "aks-gpu-spot-sc72l-divyam-prod-k8s-cluster"
      ],
      "defaults": [
        "aks-gpu-spot-glnw5-divyam-prod-k8s-cluster",
        "aks-gpu-spot-sc72l-divyam-prod-k8s-cluster"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "method",
      "prefix": "method",
      "available_values": [
        "get",
        "post"
      ],
      "defaults": [
        "get",
        "post"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "widgets": [
    {
      "id": 8748661028888002,
      "definition": {
        "title": "Overview",
        "show_title": true,
        "type": "group",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "id": 8154273677861523,
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "## Infinity Embedding Server\n\n**Deployment:** `infinity-prod-deploy`\n**Namespace:** `infinity-prod-ns`\n**Cluster:** `divyam-prod-k8s-cluster`\n**Image:** `michaelf34/infinity:0.0.76-trt-onnx`\n**GPU:** NVIDIA (spot instances)\n**Handlers:** `/embeddings`, `/health`, `/metrics`\n\n---\n*Use template variables above to filter by handler, host, or method.*",
              "background_color": "white",
              "font_size": "14",
              "text_align": "left",
              "vertical_align": "top",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 4
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 692236138166812,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Request Rate (req/s)",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "aggregator": "last",
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {
                      "comparator": ">",
                      "palette": "white_on_green",
                      "value": 0
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "palette": "white_on_red",
                      "value": 0
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1"
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "aggregator": "avg",
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "sum:infinity_prod.http_requests.count{kube_namespace:infinity-prod-ns,$handler,$host,$method}.as_rate()"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "scalar"
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 2,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "id": 3683838694423844,
            "definition": {
              "title": "Avg Latency (s)",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "aggregator": "last",
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {
                      "comparator": ">=",
                      "palette": "white_on_red",
                      "value": 1
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": ">=",
                      "palette": "white_on_yellow",
                      "value": 0.5
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": "<",
                      "palette": "white_on_green",
                      "value": 0.5
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "a / b"
                    }
                  ],
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "aggregator": "avg",
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "a",
                      "query": "sum:infinity_prod.http_request_duration_seconds.sum{kube_namespace:infinity-prod-ns,$handler,$host,$method}.as_rate()"
                    },
                    {
                      "aggregator": "avg",
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "b",
                      "query": "sum:infinity_prod.http_request_duration_seconds.count{kube_namespace:infinity-prod-ns,$handler,$host,$method}.as_rate()"
                    }
